title: [Bloodriven Village, Gloam Pike]
description: Battered cobblestones line the muddy roadway, wispy weeds poking out between wide gaps.  Broken glass bottles have been swept haphazardly against the side of the battered stone wall marking the outer border of the village, thick forests blocking any visibility beyond.

Slush-covered cobblestones line the muddy roadway, heavy iron braziers poking out between wide gaps.  Tall holly bushes have been lined against the side of the battered stone wall marking the outer border of the village, thick forests blocking any visibility beyond.
